\c 19
\s Amazwi omprofethi uJehu
\p
\v 1 UJehoshafathi inkosi yakoJuda wasebuyela endlini yakhe ngokuthula eJerusalema\x + 18.31.\x*.
\v 2 UJehu indodana kaHanani\x + 1 Kho. 16.1.\x* umboni wasephuma ukumhlangabeza\x + 1 Lan. 29.29.\x*, wathi enkosini uJehoshafathi: Unganceda yini omubi, uthande labo abazonda iN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 18.1. 20.37. 1 Kho. 22.44. Hlab. 139.21. 2 Kor. 6.14.\x*? Ngenxa yalokhu-ke kulolaka phezu kwakho oluvela ebusweni beN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 19.10. 24.18.\x*.
\v 3 Loba kunjalo izinto ezinhle zitholwe kuwe\x + 12.12. 1 Kho. 14.13.\x*, ngoba ususile izixuku elizweni\x + 17.4,6.\x*, walungisa inhliziyo yakho ukumdinga uNkulunkulu\x + 12.14. 30.19. 20.33. 1 Sam. 7.3.\x*.
\v 4 UJehoshafathi wasehlala eJerusalema; wabuya waphuma \add wahamba\add* phakathi kwabantu, kusukela eBherishebha\x + 2 Sam. 3.10.\x* kusiya entabeni yakoEfrayimi, wababuyisela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, uNkulunkulu waboyise\x + 15.8. 25.13.\x*.
\s UJehoshafathi umisa abahluleli
\p
\v 5 Wasemisa abahluleli elizweni\x + Dute. 16.18.\x* kuyo yonke imizi ebiyelweyo yakoJuda, kumuzi ngomuzi\x + 17.2.\x*.
\v 6 Wasesithi kubahluleli: Bonani elikwenzayo, ngoba kalehluleleli umuntu kodwa iN\nd kosi\nd*, elani endabeni yokwahlulela\x + 19.8. Dute. 1.17.\x*.
\v 7 Ngakho-ke uvalo ngeN\nd kosi\nd* kalube phezu kwenu, linanzelele likwenze, ngoba eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu wethu kakulabubi\x + Dute. 32.4. Jobe 8.3. 34.10. Roma 9.14.\x* lokukhangela ubuso lokwemukela izivalamlomo\x + Dute. 10.17.\x*.
\p
\v 8 Futhi leJerusalema uJehoshafathi wasemisa \add abanye\add* kumaLevi labapristi lakunhloko zaboyise zakoIsrayeli\x + 17.7,8.\x* kusahlulelo seN\nd kosi\nd* lakumibango, sebebuyele eJerusalema\x + 19.8. Dute. 1.17.\x*.
\v 9 Wasebalaya esithi: Lizakwenza njalo ekuyesabeni iN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 2 Sam. 23.3. Eks. 18.21.\x*, ngobuqotho langenhliziyo epheleleyo\x + 1 Kho. 8.61.\x*.
\v 10 Lawuphi umbango oza kini ovela kubafowenu abahlala emizini yabo, phakathi kwegazi legazi, phakathi komthetho lomlayo, izimiso lezahlulelo\x + Dute. 17.8.\x*, lizabaxwayisa ukuze bangabi lecala eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + Eks. 18.20.\x*, lolaka lwehlele phezu kwenu laphezu kwabafowenu\x + 19.2.\x*. Lizakwenza njalo, futhi lingabi lacala\x + Hez. 3.18.\x*.
\v 11 Khangelani-ke, uAmariya umpristi oyinhloko uphezu kwenu\x + 1 Lan. 6.11.\x* kulo lonke udaba lukaJehova\x + 1 Lan. 26.32.\x*, loZebhadiya indodana kaIshmayeli, umbusi wendlu yakoJuda, kulo lonke udaba lwenkosi; labaphathi amaLevi baphambi kwenu. Qinani likwenze; iN\nd kosi\nd*-ke izakuba lolungileyo\x + 1 Lan. 26.32.\x*.